			<div class="sub-wrapper">

				<div id="content">
					<h2>
	Rudolph Technologies, Inc. is a leader in the design, development, manufacture and support of defect inspection, lithography, process control metrology, and data analysis systems and software used by microelectronic device manufacturers worldwide.</h2>
<p>
	Rudolph is a public company, listed on the NYSE National Market as RTEC. It is headquartered in Wilmington, MA. The company is comprised of three business units: the Process Control Group, located in Bloomington, MN; the Lithography Systems Group, located in Wilmington, MA; and the Integrated Solutions Group, located in Tewksbury, MA. In addition, an extensive global network of sales, service, and applications offices are located in New Jersey, Texas, Europe, Korea, Taiwan, Japan, Singapore, and China.</p>

									
				</div>
				
